      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING URBAN (5) steps out for the first time at this course. Comes here a last start placegetter at Q Parklands in a OPEN (29.78). Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from two starts. Must come into calculations. HEY ERNIE (4) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including five wins and three placings. Placed last time (18.91) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 4 lengths. Looks one of the chances. PERFECT POSE (2) has been out of the placings last two but shapes well for this if she can recapture her quick win a few runs back, getting around this track over 350m in 18.99. Expecting another bold showing. MANILA PHANTOM (8) hit the frame here last start so don't underestimate.",
